		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		"More AI Manipulation: Messing with the CPU Racers is a lot of fun because of how much you can do with them. Some of their tricks were manipulated by me so that only the most impressive tricks would be shown.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		"Better Glitch Execution: Such as submarines: In my previous TAS i would always get stunned before going into a submarine. Now with a different type of sled "stuns" are no longer required. 
		$LF
	]li
