[h4 id=Tricks 
	"Tricks
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"17 different tricks can be performed by holding either L2 and R2 or both and using the D-Pad to input the trick while your sled is in the air. Trick Points range from 100 to 1500.
	$LF
	"Tricks are used to gain points in the Championship to buy upgrades for your vehicle. Some tricks can also be "held" to increase the amount of points you get. 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Tricks can be combo'd together, f.e. One Footed Can Can into Superman. These combos are relatively easy to do because they are on the same shoulder button (R2). Tricks that use the R2 button can be combo'd together with ones that use the L2 button and vice versa, but they are frameperfect. There is no reason to do tricks other than aesthetics or to emote.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"How to hold a trick?
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Example: Look Back: L2 + Up (Hold the later part of the trick so in this case "Up"). You also have to hold the respective shoulder button "L2". 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"One Footed Can-Can One Hander: R2 + Lower left (Hold lower left)
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"One Handed Superman: R2 + Upper left - Right (Hold right)
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		"Tricklist...Here are the tricks and some combos:
