	$LF
	"I exit the shortcut and i could do a trick here or some snaking, but i wanted the focus to be on the CPU Racers. Tracy crashes and i bonk Ryan so that he pushes me over when i cross the finish line. I sacrificed a 1:28:28 time for this.
